### **Database Integration Strategy**
```python
# Example: Agent with custom fields
class Agent(Base):
    __tablename__ = 'agents'
    # ... existing fields
    
    # Relationship to custom field values
    custom_field_values = relationship(
        "CustomFieldValue",
        primaryjoin="and_(Agent.id == CustomFieldValue.entity_id, "
                   "CustomFieldValue.entity_type == 'agent')",
        foreign_keys="CustomFieldValue.entity_id"
    )
